      "x": 1350, "y": 820, "width": 306, "height": 76,
      "text": "// access token  (header alg: RS256)\n{ \"iss\": \"https://auth.example.com\",\n  \"sub\": \"user-42\", \"type\": \"access\",\n  \"aud\": \"https://gw…/mcp/gitea\",\n  \"scope\": \"mcp:gitea\", \"exp\": 1700… }",
