      "x": 660, "y": 1086, "width": 240, "height": 116,
      "text": "⑤  VERIFY — offline, per request\n  ✓ signature · JWKS · RS* only\n  ✓ iss · exp · type = access\n  ✓ scope ⊇ required_scopes\n  ✓ aud  (require_audience)\n  ✗ HS256 forgery → 401",
      "originalText": "⑤  VERIFY — offline, per request\n  ✓ signature · JWKS · RS* only\n  ✓ iss · exp · type = access\n  ✓ scope ⊇ required_scopes\n  ✓ aud  (require_audience)\n  ✗ HS256 forgery → 401",
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#34d399", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid",
